<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Test Report - <%= projectName %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #bdc3c7;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #34495e;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .note {
            background-color: #fce4ec;
            color: #c2185b;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #c2185b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .offer-link {
            background-color: #f7f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .pass { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
        .fail { color: #c0392b; font-weight: bold; }
        .na { color: #7f8c8d; font-weight: bold; }
        ul { padding-left: 20px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 5px; }
        
        /* Screenshot Formatting like Reference PDF */
        .screenshot-container {
            margin: 15px 0 30px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .screenshot-container img {
            max-width: 90%;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: block;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .screenshot-caption {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 11px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Automated Test Report: <%= projectName %></h1>

    <div class="note">
        Note: According to the discussion with the developer, only robots.txt and HTTPS is checked for security testing in this test report.
    </div>

    <h2>[A] Offer Funnel</h2>
    <div class="offer-link">
        <strong>URL:</strong> <a href="<%= offerUrl %>"><%= offerUrl %></a>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <% if (funnelNotes.length > 0) { %>
            <% funnelNotes.forEach((note, index) => { %>
                <li><%= index + 1 %>. <%= note %></li>
            <% }); %>
        <% } %>
    </ul>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <h2>Usability (Desktop and Mobile)</h2>
    <h3>Devices and Browsers</h3>
    
    <!-- Windows Desktop -->
    <ul>
        <li>1. Windows - Chrome, Firefox, Microsoft Edge Chromium <span class="<%= usability.windows.status.toLowerCase() %>"><%= usability.windows.status %></span>
            <ul>
                <li>The images are pixelated</li>
                <li>The images should be middle aligned</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <% if (images && images.desktop) { %>
        <div class="screenshot-container">
            <img src="<%= images.desktop %>" alt="Desktop Screenshot" />
            <div class="screenshot-caption">Fig 1: Windows Desktop Context</div>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- Mac Desktop -->
    <ul>
        <li>2. Mac - Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Microsoft Edge Chromium <span class="<%= usability.mac.status.toLowerCase() %>"><%= usability.mac.status %></span></li>
    </ul>

    <!-- iOS Section -->
    <ul>
        <li>3. iOS -
            <ul>
                <li>A) iPad 6th Gen or iPad Mini4, iPad Pro, iPad Air <span class="<%= usability.ios.ipad.toLowerCase() %>"><%= usability.ios.ipad %></span>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Blank space showing below footer</li>
                    </ul>
                    <% if (images && images.ipad) { %>
                        <div class="screenshot-container">
                            <img src="<%= images.ipad %>" alt="iPad Screenshot" style="max-width: 60%;" />
                            <div class="screenshot-caption">Fig 2: iPad Layout Issue</div>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </li>

                <li>B) iPhone 7 or 8, iPhone 13 or 12, iPhone 14 Pro Max, iPhone 16 Plus or iPhone 15 Plus <span class="<%= usability.ios.iphone.toLowerCase() %>"><%= usability.ios.iphone %></span>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The placeholder is showing cropped</li>
                        <li>The cross icon needs to be middle aligned</li>
                    </ul>
                    <% if (images && images.iphone) { %>
                        <div class="screenshot-container">
                            <img src="<%= images.iphone %>" alt="iPhone Screenshot" style="max-width: 45%;" />
                            <div class="screenshot-caption">Fig 3: iPhone Layout Issue</div>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <!-- Android Section -->
    <ul>
        <li>4. Android
            <ul>
                <li>A) Samsung Galaxy s9 TAB <span class="<%= usability.android.tablet.toLowerCase() %>"><%= usability.android.tablet %></span></li>
                <li>B) Pixel 9, Galaxy S21 FE, Galaxy A13 <span class="<%= usability.android.phone.toLowerCase() %>"><%= usability.android.phone %></span>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The pop up should fit inside a single window</li>
                    </ul>
                    <% if (images && images.android) { %>
                        <div class="screenshot-container">
                            <img src="<%= images.android %>" alt="Android Screenshot" style="max-width: 45%;" />
                            <div class="screenshot-caption">Fig 4: Android Viewport Overlap</div>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>


    <h3>5. In-app browser testing for Android and IOS devices both <span class="pass">PASS</span></h3>
    <ul>
        <li>A. Facebook. (Test The offer Site by appending the Affiliate ID in the offer link)</li>
        <li>B. Skype (Check the Thumbnail in the chat window)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>6. Dark Mode</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>A. Android (Both in A13 and S21 FE)</li>
        <li>B. Ios (Any of the iPhone 12/13/14 Promax)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>7. IOS/Android zoom issue <span class="<%= usability.zoomIssue.toLowerCase() %>"><%= usability.zoomIssue %></span></h3>
    <p>Steps for IOS and Android verified.</p>

    <h3>8. Open Graph Information for Multiple Social Media Platforms: <span class="pass">PASS</span></h3>
    <p>Report Link Generated via www.opengraph.xyz</p>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <h2>UI/UX Friendliness and Responsiveness (Desktop and Mobile)</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>1. Different form elements, placeholders, and labels visible: <span class="<%= uiUx.formElements.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.formElements %></span></li>
        <li>2. Action buttons should be properly accessible based on the viewport: <span class="<%= uiUx.buttonsAccessible.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.buttonsAccessible %></span></li>
        <li>3. Quickly visible spelling & grammar: <span class="<%= uiUx.spelling.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.spelling %></span></li>
        <li>4. Tab indexing: <span class="<%= uiUx.tabIndexing.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.tabIndexing %></span></li>
        <li>5. Privacy/terms/contact/Error popup visibility context: <span class="<%= uiUx.popups.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.popups %></span></li>
        <li>6. Favicon check: <span class="<%= uiUx.favicon.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.favicon %></span></li>
        <li>7. Responsiveness Check with the help of browser emulation: <span class="<%= uiUx.responsiveness.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.responsiveness %></span></li>
        <li>8. In the Footer Section Copyright Should be properly mentioned: <span class="<%= uiUx.copyright.toLowerCase() %>"><%= uiUx.copyright %></span></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Functional (Desktop and Mobile)</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>1. Mandatory and optional field validation: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>2. Field allowed character length validation: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>3. Field type-wise value validation: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>4. Proper error messages should be showing: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
        <li>5. Proper Error message should appear after processing order with Decline card: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
        <li>6. Country-wise proper state population: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
        <li>7. Country-wise zip code validation: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>8. City and state auto-population according to zip code: <span class="na">NA</span></li>
        <li>9. Check whether the order is processed or not for the stateless country: <span class="na">NA</span></li>
        <li>10. Input masking for phone no: <span class="na">NA</span></li>
        <li>11. Input masking for Canada zip code: <span class="na">NA</span></li>
        <li>12. Xverify functionality test: <span class="na">NA</span></li>
        <li>13. Session Testing: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>15. Prospect form after product selection page constraints: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>16. Check the card expiry date for a one-time product ahead of current date: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>17. Credit card validation and placeholder: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>19. PayPal payment option on checkout: <span class="na">NA</span></li>
        <li>20. Apple Pay, Google Pay and Paypal redirection: <span class="na">NA</span></li>
        <li>21. Back via Browser back button constraint: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <h2>CRM End check (Desktop and Mobile)</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>2. Check the flows working properly with their campaign ID (Desktop and Mobile) <br><br>
            <strong>Note:</strong> Products are being placed under the Main Campaign in CRM instead of the Decline Campaign as mentioned in the email.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Console Issues (Desktop and Mobile)</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>A. 404 Issues in JS Console: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
        <li>B. Javascript Uncaught Exceptions
            <ul>
                <li>Desktop: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
                <li>Mobile: <span class="pass">PASS</span> (No issue found)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>C. Verify that Ajax Should not trigger Multiple Times
            <ul>
                <li>Desktop: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
                <li>Mobile: <span class="fail">FAIL</span></li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Security and Performance</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>1. On page load, the URL should force to HTTPS: <span class="<%= autoChecks.https.toLowerCase() %>"><%= autoChecks.https %></span></li>
        <li>2. Robots.txt check: <span class="<%= autoChecks.robotsTxt.toLowerCase() %>"><%= autoChecks.robotsTxt %></span></li>
        <li>3. SSl checking: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
        <li>4. SEO checking: <span class="pass">PASS</span></li>
    </ul>

</body>
</html>
